    {
      "content": "写那个吃了的社会。、",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "写少女被同化。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "最后成为了封建社会的一环。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "一个不讨喜，不符合市场，不合格的小说。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "但是，我想试试。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为，这是我的小说，我想表达的话。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
